title: These Are Some Seriously Weird Family Dynamics! Can you Guess Them?
description:
There are some really crazy family dynamics in this world, a lot of which you can find on social media. Moe challenges The Bert Show with these weird family dynamics he found on Instagram. Can you make sense of what either of these women is saying?
